<lb ed="I" n="0166c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0166c0101">大齊天保九年歲次戊寅二月八日魯思明敬造
<lb ed="I" n="0166c02" type="honorific"/>夫玄途杳邁。愛馳馹於苦津。太<note n="0166001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31166"/>＝冥【史】</note><app n="0166001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31166"/></rdg></app>虛<note n="0166002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡧯＝寂【史】</note><app n="0166002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡧯</rdg></app>。甘有作於造□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c03" type="honorific"/>照。使昏夜永幽。為<note n="0166003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB04490"/>＝屯【史】</note><app n="0166003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">屯</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB04490"/></rdg></app>雲而翳景。伏寶盈家。為无明以□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c04" type="honorific"/>能人。睹出沒之<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>常。<note n="0166004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">狑＝怜【史】</note><app n="0166004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">怜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">狑</rdg></app>六趣之苦毒。懷慈悲於大千。□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c05" type="honorific"/>十方。定靈基於運未之初。吐神源於<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>始之際。披惠□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c06" type="honorific"/>解於<note n="0166005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">仾＝低【史】</note><app n="0166005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">低</lem><rdg wit="【原】">仾</rdg></app>枝。內鏡三明。外運六通。曠<app type="star" corresp="#0166002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡧯</rdg></app><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>為。開万法之□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c07" type="honorific"/><note n="0166006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">皷＝鼓【史】</note><app n="0166006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">皷</rdg></app>。一鳴則九會俱悟。故移駕鹿苑。唱四<note n="0166007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31166"/>＝真【史】</note><app n="0166007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">真</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31166"/></rdg></app>之玄。迴<note n="0166008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨋏＝軫【史】</note><app n="0166008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨋏</rdg></app>□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c08" type="honorific"/>宣二常之極。可謂玄宗云舉。眾目備張矣。故能頃濁波．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c09" type="honorific"/>四非會於涅槃。九源以茲斷流。三障用斯雲掃。自非靈．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c10" type="honorific"/>既周。應緣異域。忻悮覺花。遊神更迹。遂使真儀匿曜。□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c11" type="honorific"/>栴檀。今正法摧<note n="0166009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB13054"/>＝綱【史】</note><app n="0166009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">綱</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB13054"/></rdg></app>。經像獎世。十力慧日。沉暉唯遠。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>明．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c12" type="honorific"/>斯弘業。紹隆三寶者哉。然摩訶上士。姓魯。名文。字字道．．．。
<lb ed="I" n="0166c13" type="honorific"/>俾侯於東國。奕世上公。著<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">夫</unclear>春秋。大漢初基。復封世祖．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c14" type="honorific"/>劫。積惠種於遐代。抱明珠以鎮心。佩白日而照物。稟□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c15" type="honorific"/>能建卓爾之願。秀於眾人之上。立希有之功。挺在群□．．．。
<lb ed="I" n="0166c16" type="honorific"/>空。行合等心。一時俱唱。遂捨伽藍地。<note n="0166010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30961"/>＝南【史】</note><app n="0166010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">南</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30961"/></rdg></app>區立寺置僧□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c17" type="honorific"/>田。於是近者不勸而來。遠方自率而至。合邑千人共□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c18" type="honorific"/>八繡像一區。合有千佛。人中石像兩區。寶車一乘。龍□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c19" type="honorific"/>□得度飾。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">運</unclear>至難辭。時來叵抑。春秋年七十有五。寢□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c20" type="honorific"/>汪汪之風。早令童年。珪璋之稱。遍滿人口。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">纂</unclear>脩父業。□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c21" type="honorific"/>圓滿。巧圖妙狀。八十種好充備。即是正覺。再顯於道□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c22" type="honorific"/>建寶塔三區。昇玉塼以<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">構</unclear>宇。磨碧石而<note n="0166011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30962"/>＝營【史】</note><app n="0166011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30962"/></rdg></app>基。隆崇聳□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c23" type="honorific"/>荊崑請工。極於人□。彫飾綺麗。踰普光之妙<note n="0166012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30963"/>＝貌【史】</note><app n="0166012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">貌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30963"/></rdg></app>。剬琴□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c24" type="honorific"/>抽榦而陵雲。或<app type="star" corresp="#0166005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">低</lem><rdg wit="【原】">仾</rdg></app>柯以<note n="0166013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦿔＝蔽【史】</note><app n="0166013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦿔</rdg></app>日。花草色色而斒爛。百菓□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c25" type="honorific"/>行路者。仰聖顏而徘徊。稽首者。慕靈容而頌歎。其地□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c26" type="honorific"/>則山川之爽塏。土地之沃壤。万物饒演。人豐禮讓。宅□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c27" type="honorific"/>化。六合寧一。中宮內外。宰相群官。州郡令長。忠貞職□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c28" type="honorific"/>彌勒三會。俱逢上首。逮及法界有形。普同斯福。乃作□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c29" type="honorific"/>文像東行。授記彌勒。下濟群盲。戀心仰慕。圖寫真靈。□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c30" type="honorific"/>神。靈相在中。雖未宣化。氣澤流風。其二<note n="0166014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30964"/>＝茫【史】</note><app n="0166014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">茫</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30964"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0166014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">茫</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30964"/></rdg></app>易遠。龍運□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0166c31" type="honorific"/>挺絕。持一无雙。其三奇哉大士。唯魯道惠。練解苦空。志□．．．</p>
